latestIgtvVideos.title: Tati’s Eco-Sanctuary Collection
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Earth Day and every day, join us in taking steps to protect our planet; the sanctuary we all love.

INTRODUCING THE TATI ECO-SANCTUARY COLLECTION 
Inspired by the beautiful, delicate, and vulnerable environment of @tatiwest home island of Kauai, we are proud to introduce Tatiana Weston-Webb's new Eco Sanctuary Collection. A line of performance swimwear designed, sourced, and responsibly manufactured using recycled materials to limit environmental impact while promoting eco-conscious consumption.
 
"Not a day goes by that I don't find a new appreciation for home and this entire earth," Tatiana Weston-Webb

EARLY ACCESS: Sign up for our newsletter to get first dibs on our new eco-friendly Tatiana Weston-Webb swimwear collection! (Link in story)
 
Tati’s Eco-Sanctuary Collection will be available in early May 2021.

🎥@gregsworld
